# Toolchain Policy: npm + eslint + jest (JavaScript)

| Role | Tool |
|---|---|
| Package manager | `npm` |
| Formatter | `prettier` |
| Linter | `eslint` |
| Test runner | `jest` |

## Key commands

```bash
npm install --save-dev eslint prettier jest
npm test
npm run lint
npm run format
```
